I followed these instructions to create a 'rebarabbit.service' that will start automatically on the server.

`https://hackernoon.com/making-node-js-service-always-alive-on-ubuntu-server-e20c9c0808e4`

## To Start the service run
```
sudo systemctl start rebarabit.service
```

## To Stop the service run
```
sudo systemctl stop rebarabbit.service
```

## To restart service run
```
sudo systemctl restart rebarabbit.service
```
